            <V n="text" t="variation">
              <U n="variation">
                <L n="variations">
                  <T>0x2C7F7E1<!--Everybody seems to have theories about who my real dad is, like it's their business. The funny thing is, sometimes when I'm walking around, I'll see a weird reflection of a black cloak behind me. I feel a really strange tie to the idea of death and reaping. Wait, not creepy like that, I mean...well, just the idea of Grim is something, huh? --></T>
                  <T>0x3DD3CDC4<!--The other day, the TV was on the fritz and it electrocuted me. Out of nowhere, there's Layne just standing there saying, "Watch yourself, kid, you'll die of electrocution if you're not careful" in this dreamy voice. I wonder if all his little fans know that the eccentric musician act is absolutely not an act.--></T>
                  <T>0x643EA3D0<!--Zelmira got way into that tarot stuff a while back and got me all interested in the Order of Lenore stuff. You know about that, right? It was appealing to me, cuz I feel like I'm just always in some random danger that I can't predict or understand. Tarot gives me a sense of order, I think? Or it makes things feel less chaotic. Whatever, I just like it a lot. You've gotten cards and seen the tomes around Ravenwood and all that, right?--></T>
                </L>
              </U>
            </V>
            <V n="title" t="enabled">
