                  <T>0x948AF48<!--I've honestly been really lonely since my best friend Pascal moved. I mean the guy basically disappeared off the map! Deleted his Social Bunny and everything. It's how I ended up talking to Edith so much. I kept going for walks all by myself and trying to talk to her. Not like I had anyone else, you know?--></T>
